It can be traded like a moving average

271
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:24,240
or as a dynamic support and resistance.

272
00:10:24,880 --> 00:10:27,340
Volume Profiles – It displays a volume bar

273
00:10:27,340 --> 00:10:29,820
horizontally, which can be treated as key levels

274
00:10:29,820 --> 00:10:31,480
for potential entry positions.

275
00:10:32,580 --> 00:10:35,580
Supply and Demand – Also referred to as

276
00:10:35,580 --> 00:10:38,600
order blocks, these are zones where significant price

277
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:39,680
movements have occurred.

278
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:42,460
If price moves significantly upwards from a level,

279
00:10:42,740 --> 00:10:45,160
it is considered a demand zone, and if

280
00:10:45,160 --> 00:10:47,800
price moves significantly downwards from a level, it

281
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:49,260
is considered a supply zone.

282
00:10:49,780 --> 00:10:52,100
Just like support and resistance, these zones can

283
00:10:52,100 --> 00:10:54,400
be treated as key levels for potential entry

284
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:55,020
positions.

285
00:10:55,760 --> 00:10:58,980
Market Structure – Market structure is when a

286
00:10:58,980 --> 00:11:02,080
trader analyzes the behavior, condition, and flow of

287
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:02,460
the market.

288
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:05,880
An uptrend structure is characterized by price forming

289
00:11:05,880 --> 00:11:09,220
higher highs and higher lows, while downtrend structure

290
00:11:09,220 --> 00:11:12,020
is characterized by price forming lower highs and

291
00:11:12,020 --> 00:11:12,620
lower lows.

292
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:16,280
Break of Structure – It is when price

293
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:18,720
breaks the previous price peak during a trend.

294
00:11:19,020 --> 00:11:21,300
For example, if the price forms a higher

295
00:11:21,300 --> 00:11:23,540
highs and higher lows, this break of the

296
00:11:23,540 --> 00:11:25,440
previous highs is called break of structure.

297
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:29,280
Change of Character – It occurs when price

298
00:11:29,280 --> 00:11:32,060
breaks the previous structure during a trend, often

299
00:11:32,060 --> 00:11:34,420
signaling a reversal from that current trend.

300
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:37,040
For example, if the price is forming higher

301
00:11:37,040 --> 00:11:39,180
highs and higher lows, then it breaks the

302
00:11:39,180 --> 00:11:41,860
previous lows forming lower lows, this is called

303
00:11:41,860 --> 00:11:42,840
a change of character.

